  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As you hit with a weapon attack or unarmed strike, your strike rings with thunder that is audible within 300 feet of you, and the attack deals an extra [[/r 1d8]] plus your spellcasting ability modifier thunder damage to the target. Additionally, if the target is a creature, it must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be knocked prone, and if you choose, is knocked 10 feet away from you.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels</strong>. When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the extra damage dealt by the attack increases by [[/r 1d8]] for each slot.</p>",
